# Python Function :
Function is a group related statmenets  that specific task

Syntax:

def function_name(parameters):
    """
        doc string
    """

    statement(s)

# def - keyword
# parameters(arguments)  - which we pass to value to a function
# : mark end of function header
# Doc string - documentation string
# statement(s) - return statement to return the value from the function

# return statement:
return statement is used to exit a function  and go back to the place
from where it was called.

Syntax:
    return (expression )


# Python Lambda function
 lambda function which is also called the anonymous function
Syntax
 lambda: arguments: expression

 # lambda - keyword
 # arguments - function will recieve
 # expression - whose result is the return value of the function

# Python Decorator
# Decorator - Can be thought of as function which modify the functionlity
of another function
